          <label for="comment">Reason:</label>
          <select id="flagging_flag_id" name="flagging[flag_id]">
            <option value="1">spam</option>
            <option value="2">troll</option>
            <option value="4">inappropriate</option>
          </select>
        </fieldset>
        <fieldset class="s-fieldset">
          <label for="flagging[comment]">Notes:</label>
          <textarea cols="50" id="flagging_comment" name="flagging[comment]" rows="5"></textarea>
        </fieldset>
        <div class="col short-note">
          <p>Your flag will not be visible to anyone but moderators. Please select the reason you are flagging this content: spam, trolling or just inappropriate. Then write us a short note explaining why you flagged it that way.</p>
